<!-- ##### MACRO CAIRO_HAS_IMAGE_SURFACE ##### -->
<para>
Defined if the image surface backend is available.
The image surface backend is always built in.
This macro was added for completeness in cairo 1.8.
</para>

@Since: 1.8


